data.description: Discover this charming brick home that effortlessly combines comfort and style. Featuring 3 bedrooms, a recently remodeled bathroom with a walk-in shower, a kitchen adorned with granite countertops, tiled backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The spacious laundry room/pantry adds convenience, while the rear entrance leads to a large fenced backyard with a patio area and garden shed. Large Cement Slab to the rear of the property. Recent updates include a new 30-year roof and a fully encapsulated crawl space. Seller is also providing a 1 Year Home Warranty provided by Old Republic. Enjoy modern living in this tastefully upgraded home.
